{"tid":2007610,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭月娥稱會虛心聆聽　為社會找出路","createTime":"2020-05-08T11:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T12:04:28.000Z","uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"058bf237dd6ef4d0d921bdeae8d100b57f0106f2","tid":2007610,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:58:15.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥連同幾名司局長發表短片，回顧過去一年工作和提出新年希望。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，社會動盪持續超過半年，作為特首責無旁貸，她會虛心聆聽，為社會找出路。<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波說，過去1年內憂外患，經濟受沉重打擊，只要恢復社會秩序就可以跨過眼前困難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uV0WfdYV5Oo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuV0WfdYV5Oo&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=fb549a57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uV0WfdYV5Oo</a><br />\n<br />\n虛心聆聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1JJzGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1JJzGF.jpg&h=6cf3923a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8ZQeG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8ZQeG0.jpg&h=78658b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkAvY82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdkAvY82.jpg&h=83a42970&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d814616e183901a0cb95b46cabaa09ec6903bdad","tid":2007610,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"打錯字<br />\n虛<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>偽</strong></span>聆聽"},{"pid":"0c63d4c4661cef332c30172da86f115beb1be9d9","tid":2007610,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"心虛零聽"},{"pid":"e5d6071b96f14318284ceaefb928f599ec303e94","tid":2007610,"uid":259402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"單向聆聽"}]}